Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(OP)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.02,0:02:11.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露莉亞在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.52,0:02:16.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 看來有點做過頭了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.01,0:02:19.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.54,0:02:22.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這時機真是無可挑剔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.99,0:02:28.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這裡的實驗也結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.58,0:02:31.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回收這玩意兒後趕緊收隊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.79,0:02:32.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.15,0:02:35.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡！肆意妄為的混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.46,0:02:36.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們不單單污染了我們的海洋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.01,0:02:38.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還將我們的城鎮搞成一團糟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.79,0:02:39.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡直天理難…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.60,0:02:41.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.61,0:02:43.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請不要對他們做過分的事！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.46,0:02:44.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,過分的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.93,0:02:46.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.33,0:02:48.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對於這個島的人來說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.82,0:02:52.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特別是那些年輕人來說 簡直是天降橫禍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.43,0:02:54.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你不來這座島
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.91,0:03:00.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們就既不會受傷害也不會被逮捕了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.32,0:03:06.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 就是因為你從我們那裡逃跑了才會變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.70,0:03:07.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.32,0:03:10.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你真心為了這裡的人們著想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.63,0:03:13.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就老老實實的回到我們那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.33,0:03:18.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想去你們那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.03,0:03:23.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼你想怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.01,0:03:26.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想和大家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.68,0:03:29.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想和古蘭和卡塔莉娜一起繼續旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.87,0:03:30.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.06,0:03:32.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,旅行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.35,0:03:37.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你的這個願望我既不會考慮 也不會允許
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.96,0:03:38.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.22,0:03:42.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為你是星之民所遺留下來的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.40,0:03:46.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只為將一切破壞殆盡的工具
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.61,0:03:47.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,工具？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.73,0:03:48.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.56,0:03:51.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就和這東西一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.95,0:03:59.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要扣動扳機就可以輕易傷人 奪人性命
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.40,0:04:03.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是這樣的一個工具
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.15,0:04:04.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是工具！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.08,0:04:06.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我不會做這種事的！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.02,0:04:07.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.16,0:04:13.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來你忘記了自己是一個極其可怕的工具呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.66,0:04:19.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼就我讓你想起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.30,0:04:32.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你最初是何時看到這個光輝的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.25,0:04:34.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我記得…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.30,0:04:37.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當時除你之外還有其他實驗體來著
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.73,0:04:42.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些實驗體最後如何了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.50,0:04:44.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你對他們做了什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.03,0:04:47.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你應該記得才對
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.38,0:04:57.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想起來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.38,0:04:58.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.07,0:05:01.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是為了破壞而生的道具
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.40,0:05:03.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你所能做的只有破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.13,0:05:05.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的存在意義僅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.02,0:05:08.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作為破壞而生的道具
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.29,0:05:14.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是不可以和那些一無所知 和平度日的人們在一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.43,0:05:16.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能去大家那裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.03,0:05:19.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你嘴裡所謂的同伴也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.21,0:05:21.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你留在他們身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.06,0:05:24.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們早晚會受盡折磨 遭遇不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.92,0:05:26.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古蘭他們也不行？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.99,0:05:30.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你會將他們所擁有的東西都破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.91,0:05:34.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連渣都不剩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.03,0:05:37.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,懂了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.08,0:05:40.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你只能和我們在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.85,0:05:45.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為只有我們才能抑制你的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.72,0:05:47.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要…我不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.12,0:05:50.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我想和大家一起！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.77,0:05:54.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手！還給我！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.25,0:06:04.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 快站起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.59,0:06:06.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別在這裡浪費時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.93,0:06:15.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.55,0:06:18.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露莉亞！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.69,0:06:21.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古蘭…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.53,0:06:25.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你對露莉亞做了什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.72,0:06:29.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是讓她想起自己是什麼東西而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.93,0:06:49.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.04,0:06:51.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道是你嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.95,0:07:03.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又打算像那時那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.69,0:07:07.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將自己以外的東西都破壞掉嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.27,0:07:07.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.73,0:07:20.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露莉亞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.72,0:07:22.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎麼了 露莉亞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.92,0:07:25.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古蘭！露莉亞！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.16,0:07:28.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.41,0:07:30.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 古蘭 你受傷了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.09,0:07:32.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 露莉亞好像不太對勁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.73,0:07:34.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎麼了 露莉亞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.46,0:07:37.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 不太妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.00,0:07:39.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼那個會出現在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.60,0:07:48.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古蘭 你想做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.23,0:07:50.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必須做點兒什麼才行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.65,0:07:52.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在不是做這些的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.67,0:07:54.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帶上露莉亞 我們暫時先撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.29,0:07:54.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.43,0:07:59.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你受傷了 而且不能就這樣放著露莉亞不管吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.88,0:08:06.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趕緊離開這裡！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.27,0:08:15.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了 趕緊去高處
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.76,0:08:46.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露莉亞！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.45,0:08:52.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 團長你又想亂來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.47,0:08:54.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作點啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.31,0:09:06.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.25,0:09:08.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這孩子挺讓人擔心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.62,0:09:10.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露莉亞！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.28,0:09:14.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之先將她轉移到安全的地方去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.43,0:09:26.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.00,0:09:27.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.47,0:09:33.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起我 露莉亞如何了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.36,0:09:35.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 卡塔莉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.51,0:09:36.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們可以進去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.48,0:09:37.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.06,0:09:40.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露莉亞如何了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.66,0:09:47.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露莉亞…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.45,0:09:52.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這小妹妹到底怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.27,0:09:54.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然看上去像是在睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.30,0:09:57.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是不管我怎麼叫也叫不醒她
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.03,0:10:01.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,治療魔法也沒用 為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.89,0:10:04.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道被剛才的怪物做了什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.19,0:10:06.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個魔物到底是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.08,0:10:09.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歐根 你應該知道些什麼的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.79,0:10:10.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.53,0:10:11.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是…剛剛那位？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.78,0:10:12.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫蘿賽塔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.36,0:10:15.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算是他們的熟人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.21,0:10:22.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說歐根知道那東西是什麼意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.83,0:10:24.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那條龍是這座島的守護者
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.19,0:10:29.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掌控生命之海的大星晶獸 利維坦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.87,0:10:33.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你久居在這裡 應該有見過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.84,0:10:37.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是海洋的守護神？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.20,0:10:42.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想是因為帝國的實驗導致海洋不斷被污染
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.07,0:10:45.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從而使他變成了那個樣子的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.05,0:10:50.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 露莉亞現在這個狀況和利維坦有關聯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.45,0:10:52.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.55,0:10:56.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這與露莉亞自身所發生的異常沒任何關係
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.67,0:10:58.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說異常？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.03,0:11:00.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露莉亞到底怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.30,0:11:03.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她為了保護什麼而封閉了內心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.44,0:11:06.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切斷了一切呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.54,0:11:10.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣一來 魔法和藥品都無法治癒她
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.22,0:11:11.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼？為什麼會這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.29,0:11:14.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要如何才能喚醒她？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.72,0:11:16.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然有喚醒她的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.95,0:11:18.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但不容易
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.71,0:11:22.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且就算強行叫她起來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.72,0:11:26.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她可能又會想以另一種形式消失
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.77,0:11:27.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.80,0:11:30.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 不能就這樣放著她不管
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.28,0:11:31.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.58,0:11:33.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是就算想為她做些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.29,0:11:36.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們連跟她對話的方法都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.88,0:11:39.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟她對話…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.59,0:11:41.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的如此嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.30,0:11:50.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說不定…古蘭能行？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.41,0:11:53.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯！和她共享生命的你可以
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.05,0:11:57.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 這是只有你才能做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.31,0:12:00.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有我才能做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.89,0:12:01.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.56,0:12:06.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的目的是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.19,0:12:10.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道又是黑騎士的手下？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.29,0:12:11.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說黑騎士？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.55,0:12:14.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我不期望你會實話實說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.08,0:12:16.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你在打什麼算盤
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.34,0:12:21.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女人都會有秘密的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.25,0:12:27.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉卡姆 蘿賽塔不是我們的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.42,0:12:32.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那時候 從海浪中將我們救起的是她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.87,0:12:34.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 在波特普利茲的時候也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.20,0:12:38.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後呢 你心意如何 團長？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.96,0:12:40.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管結果如何
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.37,0:12:42.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道讓露莉亞甦醒的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.88,0:12:50.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎麼做就交給你們決定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.26,0:12:55.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想好了就來告訴我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.41,0:13:01.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.85,0:13:03.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 古蘭 要怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.85,0:13:05.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不贊成
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.66,0:13:07.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎麼說也太可疑了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.67,0:13:08.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歐根！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.58,0:13:09.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.45,0:13:10.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海水又發了變化
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.08,0:13:12.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且城裡的水也產生了異變
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.08,0:13:15.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘖 一個接著一個的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.51,0:13:16.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去看看嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.63,0:13:17.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我陪你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.03,0:13:18.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.14,0:13:21.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古蘭 你在這裡休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.40,0:13:22.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡塔莉娜也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.75,0:13:23.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但…但是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.54,0:13:24.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.75,0:13:26.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你待在露莉亞的身邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.12,0:13:36.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當我到達露莉亞身邊的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.81,0:13:39.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帝國的人好像已經對她做了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.06,0:13:42.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伯梅倫…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.53,0:13:47.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他說…「又打算像那時一樣將自己以外的東西都破壞掉嗎」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.86,0:13:49.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前也發生過這種事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.26,0:13:54.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡塔莉娜？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.83,0:13:56.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.95,0:14:02.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必須得將我們和你相遇前發生的一些事告訴你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.54,0:14:04.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我相遇之前？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.40,0:14:05.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.51,0:14:07.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帝國對露莉亞做的實驗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.54,0:14:11.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其中就發生過類似的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.10,0:14:16.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帝國軍為了開發武器
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.54,0:14:19.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對露莉亞和魔晶進行了研究
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.86,0:14:23.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在某個無人島上進行魔晶實驗的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.32,0:14:24.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發生了失控事故
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.41,0:14:28.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被植入魔晶後發狂的魔物們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.40,0:14:30.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盯上露莉亞那一剎那
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.93,0:14:31.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在此時…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.08,0:14:58.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我不知道露莉亞召喚出了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.85,0:15:00.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但那股力量的餘波
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.85,0:15:03.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓整個島嶼腐壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.41,0:15:10.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帝國馬上決定囚禁露莉亞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.53,0:15:16.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把她隔離…「保管」起來 以免她再次失控
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.45,0:15:19.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我則被選中去照顧她
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.26,0:15:25.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那時候的露莉亞毫無表情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.17,0:15:29.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都覺得她像是一個機械
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.69,0:15:31.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.22,0:15:40.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露莉亞並非沒有感情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.36,0:15:43.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她只是不知道如何去表達
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.31,0:15:49.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之後我開始教她各種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.76,0:15:54.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露莉亞開始能夠理解和感受到快樂和悲傷了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.36,0:15:56.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.15,0:15:59.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對於我講的故事 她開始抱有興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.58,0:16:03.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很快便開始對外面的世界產生了嚮往
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.61,0:16:06.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我當時就覺得如果能離開這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.21,0:16:08.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在外面的世界裡自由生活的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.42,0:16:10.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,於是我決定…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.28,0:16:14.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,後來露莉亞見到了你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.32,0:16:16.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通過和你相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.36,0:16:21.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露莉亞應該學到了我沒能教給她的重要的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.51,0:16:23.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露莉亞每天晚上都會跟我說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.93,0:16:28.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她和你還有伊歐做了什麼以及看到了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.69,0:16:29.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她非常開心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.83,0:16:32.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我對此感到很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.06,0:16:39.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我卻沒有保護好露莉亞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.33,0:16:42.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個時候我什麼都沒做到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.21,0:16:46.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 卡塔莉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.73,0:16:47.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.35,0:16:49.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.21,0:16:52.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些應該全都由我來承擔的！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.92,0:16:55.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但為什麼受傷的會是你們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.42,0:16:57.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡塔莉娜？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.34,0:17:02.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露莉亞為什麼要受這樣的苦才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.86,0:17:13.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能感受到露莉亞的感情 並很愛護她
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.77,0:17:16.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這對於從那個什麼都沒有的房間裡走出來的露莉亞來說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.66,0:17:18.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是多大的救贖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.86,0:17:23.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古蘭 你也去休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.53,0:17:24.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.90,0:17:27.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我待在露莉亞的身邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.02,0:17:35.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是古蘭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.39,0:17:36.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.68,0:17:37.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露莉亞如何了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.16,0:17:41.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.59,0:17:48.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,俺說 你在煩惱什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.94,0:17:54.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能和露莉亞對話 我該說些什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.36,0:18:00.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且她到底想保護什麼才這樣一覺不醒的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.23,0:18:03.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,俺不可能知道的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.98,0:18:06.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟不管是俺還是你都不是露莉亞嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.40,0:18:08.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.49,0:18:14.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以先聽聽她的話如何
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.54,0:18:18.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她肯定有一些對所有人都說不出口的煩惱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.60,0:18:21.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但如果問的人是你 她應該會說的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.63,0:18:27.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為你們共享生命嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.63,0:18:31.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以這正是你才能做的事 不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.75,0:18:35.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.90,0:18:38.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好和露莉亞談談
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.30,0:18:40.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把你的想法告訴她的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.34,0:18:42.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,俺覺得露莉亞一定會想回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.67,0:18:44.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.60,0:18:46.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你 碧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.18,0:18:47.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.90,0:18:54.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,俺知道 你一定能行的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.99,0:18:56.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.35,0:19:01.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是跟我走會遭遇什麼沒人會知道哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.88,0:19:03.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道 沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.01,0:19:05.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼我帶你走…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.14,0:19:09.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帶你們到能拯救她的星晶獸的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.31,0:19:10.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星晶獸…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.09,0:19:13.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我沒辦法保證會發生什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.95,0:19:16.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的生命是露莉亞分給我的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.34,0:19:19.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我一定會救她的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.33,0:19:22.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.47,0:19:25.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你打算接受那個女人的提議嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.15,0:19:27.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.19,0:19:28.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.60,0:19:32.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟目前我們也沒有其他救露莉亞的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.43,0:19:34.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能賭賭看了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.46,0:19:37.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別擔心啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.50,0:19:40.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,團長你決定去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.32,0:19:43.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就把你們安全地送到哪 這就是舵手的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.71,0:19:44.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉卡姆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.98,0:19:45.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以說…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.60,0:19:48.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夥子 不用客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.20,0:19:50.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想做什麼就做什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.61,0:19:54.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天塌下來有我們頂住
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.65,0:19:56.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我們大人的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.67,0:19:57.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.45,0:20:00.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.17,0:20:04.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.86,0:20:05.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊歐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.59,0:20:07.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,憑什麼你們就這樣決定了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.90,0:20:09.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.37,0:20:11.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是碰巧你不在…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.37,0:20:13.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽好了！露莉亞是我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.05,0:20:16.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想為她出點兒力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.75,0:20:18.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像師父幫了我一樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.82,0:20:20.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了 我知道了 你冷靜點！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.72,0:20:22.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很冷靜啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.24,0:20:24.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也一定會去的！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.29,0:20:31.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拋下我就出發的話一定不會原諒你們的！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.89,0:20:33.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.50,0:20:36.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,熊孩子真吵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.50,0:20:37.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼關係呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.26,0:20:43.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然不算團結 但你們的方向都是一致的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.45,0:20:44.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話是沒錯啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.43,0:20:49.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你 伊歐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.85,0:21:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受你照顧了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.41,0:21:01.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要出發了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.72,0:21:04.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 全都完事後我們會回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.50,0:21:06.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以大叔你也別掛掉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.79,0:21:09.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真敢說
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.81,0:21:11.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心點
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.17,0:21:13.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.24,0:21:15.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝你們好運
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.02,0:21:20.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過話說回來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.79,0:21:23.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽到消息後趕緊跑過來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.19,0:21:26.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到發生了這麼大的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.61,0:21:28.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 正如你所見到的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.75,0:21:30.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 為了修復城鎮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.63,0:21:32.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就麻煩你四處籌集各種物資了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.46,0:21:37.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不 我也是盡自己所能罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.80,0:21:39.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了 我們出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.65,0:21:41.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 不能這樣磨蹭下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.37,0:21:43.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位 出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.84,0:21:46.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蘿賽塔閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.90,0:21:48.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻煩你帶路了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.70,0:21:51.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 我們出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.72,0:21:54.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前往鬱鬱蔥蔥的島嶼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.30,0:21:55.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魯馬西群島
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.30,0:21:55.88,Default,NTP,0,120,0,,{\fs30}Lumacie
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.44,0:21:57.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魯馬西群島……
